tspan.tspan: Software competencies - as a user, developer, or proponent -
become indispensible in today's digital scientific conduct. Yet
overall, these competencies are not universally fostered in
the German academic system. In a workshop hosted by the
Volkswagen Stiftung in November 2024, 30 participants from
different scientific fields and positions developed actionable
recommendations for different target groups in or
around academia to improve digital competency
